subject: Ice Skating
Ice Dancing
lead_paragraph: The Americans Meryl Davis and Charlie White kept the ice dancing lead at Skate Canada in Ottawa by earning the best score in original dance. Davis and White led after the compulsory dance on Friday and have 90.65 points. Nathalie Pechalat and Fabian Bourzat of France are second with 81.27 points after placing sixth in original dance and second in the compulsory dance.
